<p><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">- Màu sắc: Trắng</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">- Phần thân (Upper): PU Leather + Mesh.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">- Phần đế giữa (Midsole): EVA + ENERGYMAX + Nylon Sheet.</span></span></p>
